.SH CONFORMING TO
These functions are not in POSIX.1, but
.BR setnetgrent (),
.BR endnetgrent (),
.BR getnetgrent (),
and
.BR innetgr ()
are available on most UNIX systems.
.BR getnetgrent_r ()
is not widely available on other systems.
